          [gbastien]
        
        1.3 (2015-04-15)
        ----------------
        
        - Do not reverse workflow_history in ImioHistoryAdapter.getHistory
          as it is for display purpose, do this in the IHContentHistoryView.getHistory
          [gbastien]
